window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Rapidly rising romance star Julie Anne Long is making an indelible mark with her smart, sensual, richly emotional love stories, especially her unforgettable Pennyroyal Green novels. The sixth delectable Pennyroyal Green affair, Long's<i> How the Marquess Was Won</i> is a \"keeper\" - the story of a beautiful orphan from the streets of Regency London, now refined, who inadvertently bewitches the dashing nobleman whom England's scandal sheets have dubbed \"Lord Ice.\"</p> <p>A multiple RITA Award, Romantic Times Reviewer's Choice Award, and Holt Medallion finalist, the incomparable Julie Anne Long is certain to win the hearts and eternal devotion of dedicated romance fans everywhere with <i>How the Marquess Was Won</i>.</p> <p><b>Contains mature themes.</b></p>"; 
